name.k: 多鄰國 - 極速學外語
Duolingo-英語/韓国語などのリスニングや英単語の練習

platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 英語・韓国語など40以上の言語がゲームのように学べる！

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 遊戲化學習，掌握語言技巧
寓教于乐 掌握一门新语言
A fun way to learn a language
課程循序漸進 學習外語無負擔

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: With its friendly approach and awesome updates, Duolingo’s long been one of our favorite apps for learning another language. Its secret: making the process genuinely fun. Engaging mini-games test your reading, writing, and speaking skills, and joining a club (where you can encourage and compete with others) adds a great social element. Bonus: all those languages and games are available for free!
這是我們最喜歡的外語學習 App 之一，整個過程非常有趣。更重要的是，所有語言學習材料和遊戲都是免費！
学习语言贵在坚持。这款 App 会通过游戏化课程，帮你快速入门并掌握一门语言。可别小看这只绿色小鸟，如果它发现你偷懒，后果可是很“严重”的。
One of our favourite apps for learning another language, the process is genuinely fun. What’s more, all those languages and games are available for free!
新しい言語を学習する際におすすめしたいアプリの一つです。学びのプロセスが純粋に楽しいだけでなく、どの言語学習やゲームも無料で使えます。

With its friendly approach and awesome updates, Duolingo’s long been one of our favourite apps for learning another language. Its secret: making the process genuinely fun. Engaging mini-games test your reading, writing and speaking skills, and joining a club (where you can encourage and compete with others) adds a great social element. Bonus: all those languages and games are available for free!
這款 App 讓學習語言變得像玩遊戲一樣有趣。你可以在此體驗各種語言課程與小遊戲，而且全部免費！
C’est l’une de nos apps préférées d’apprentissage de langues pour son côté vraiment ludique. Et l’intégralité des langues et jeux est gratuite !

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Learn a new language. Join a club, chat with bots, and get reminders to practice.
Learn a new language. Join a club and get reminders to practise.
